Package: WeatherSweden
Type: Package
Title: Weather Data Retrieval for Swedish Cities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mir Abdul Rehman [aut], Thor Wahlestedt [aut]
Maintainer: Mir Abdul Rehman <abdmi452@student.liu.se>, Thor Wahlestedt <thowa194@student.liu.se>
Description: Provides real-time weather data for Swedish cities using the Open-Meteo API. This package allows users to retrieve weather metrics such as temperature and windspeed for various cities in Sweden. It includes a Shiny App for visualization.
